        <div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
            <ab>
                <lb n="1"/><w part="F"><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>μοι</w>
                    <w part="I">αἰω<supplied reason="lost">νι</supplied></w><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
                <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><w part="M">ους<gap reason="illegible" quantity="2" unit="character"/></w><gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/>
            </ab>
        </div>

            <div type="translation" xml:lang="ru">
                <p>… вечн…</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <p>... etern...</p>
            </div>
            
            <div type="commentary" xml:lang="ru">
                <p>Надпись издана эпиграфическим шрифтом, без чтения дважды (Латышев 1907, 38. № 18; IOSPE I<hi rend="sup">2</hi> 626).</p>
                <p>1. Если здесь, действительно, читается типичный для ранневизантийских императорских надписей
                    (ср. <ref type="inscription">V 5</ref><!--byz004-->, <ref type="inscription">V 6</ref><!--byz005-->) 
                        эпитет αἰω[νι..., что может указывать на официальный характер надписи.</p>
                    <p>Судя по форме мю, надпись датируется византийским временем.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" xml:lang="en">
                <p>The inscription was twice published in diplomatic transcription (Latyshev 1907, No.18; IOSPE I<hi rend="sup">2</hi> 626).</p>
                <p>1. If indeed we could read here the epithet αἰω[νι..., which was typical for Early Byzantine imperial inscriptions
                    (cf. <ref type="inscription">V 5</ref><!--byz004-->, <ref type="inscription">V 6</ref><!--byz005-->), 
                this would indicate the official character of the inscription. </p>
                <p>Judging by the form of mu, the inscription is of Byzantine date.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
